<h3 id="what-to-include">What to Include</h3>

<p>Show glyphs from both families together to demonstrate how they harmonize. Set some body copy to see how it displays in longer text. Pull out some glyphs from each family to show individually so we see how they harmonize. You can provide background info on both families. Who designed them?</p>

<p>You can also describe in writing what you see being similarities with the families.</p>

